        "mainpic": "94a2f3a6-4862-4bbf-a42f-b3b9dbfbd501",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 1000 Sq. Ft. Visit This Website to See More: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/qv4wbr Call Now - show contact info x 34 OR Text 34 to show contact info to contact our leasing team. Experience Harlo Apartments Community Info: Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Features: ‣  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ‣  Controlled access buildings ‣  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ‣  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Dishwasher available in select homes ‣  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ‣  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove Community Amenities: ‣  Pet friendly community ‣  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ‣  Professional onsite management team ‣  Flex rental payments ‣  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ‣  Open parking and carports ‣  On-site resident storage ‣  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ‣  Updater application ‣  BILT payment center ‣  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ‣  Easy highway access ‣  Online resident portal ‣  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ‣  Package receiving Pet Policy: We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements: Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Equal Housing Opportunity 7cIao29Kn",
