        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Call Now - show contact info x 179 OR Text 179 to show contact info to contact our team. Follow The Link Below: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/0iy5se APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS 1 bedroom | 1 bath | 625 square feet Features ✓  Gas range in all apartment homes ✓  Beautiful courtyard views available ✓  Spacious closets ✓  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✓  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ✓  Dishwashers available in select homes ✓  On-site resident storage included ✓  Heated hallways ✓  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer ✓  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ✓  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ✓  Indoor mailboxes ✓  Walk-in closets in select homes ✓  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✓  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet Community Features ✓  Flex rental payments ✓  Updater application ✓  Online resident portal ✓  24-hour maintenance response guarantee ✓  Covered parking ✓  On-site resident storage ✓  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ✓  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ✓  Beautiful, mature landscape ✓  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall ✓  BILT payment center ✓  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ✓  Expansive community clubhouse ✓  Professional onsite management team ✓  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ✓  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ✓  Package receiving Community Info Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home. Pet Policy Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Office Hours Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity IpcW4DPj95",
