        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Follow This Link for More Information: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/aazzgu Call Now - show contact info x 258 OR Text 258 to show contact info to text our team. Experience Harlo Apartments 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 800 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ✧  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✧  Controlled access buildings ✧  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ✧  Dishwasher available in select homes ✧  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ✧  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ✧  Updated lighting fixtures throughout Community Highlights ✧  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ✧  Online resident portal ✧  Updater application ✧  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ✧  BILT payment center ✧  Open parking and carports ✧  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ✧  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ✧  Easy highway access ✧  Pet friendly community ✧  Package receiving ✧  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ✧  Professional onsite management team ✧  Flex rental payments ✧  On-site resident storage Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Equal Housing Opportunity HVssY3Oa9",
