        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 800 Use the link below for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/jzyev7 APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS Call Now - show contact info x 178 OR Text 178 to show contact info for more information.   Community Info Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home. Residence Features ✩  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✩  Gas range in all apartment homes ✩  Walk-in closets in select homes ✩  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ✩  On-site resident storage included ✩  Spacious closets ✩  Beautiful courtyard views available ✩  Indoor mailboxes ✩  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✩  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ✩  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ✩  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer ✩  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✩  Heated hallways ✩  Dishwashers available in select homes ✩  Brick buildings and traditional architecture Community Features ✩  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall ✩  Beautiful, mature landscape ✩  Package receiving ✩  Updater application ✩  Professional onsite management team ✩  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ✩  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ✩  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ✩  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ✩  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ✩  Flex rental payments ✩  BILT payment center ✩  Online resident portal ✩  24-hour maintenance response guarantee ✩  Covered parking ✩  Expansive community clubhouse ✩  On-site resident storage Pet Policy Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Office Hours Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity TT5roZ6l8sm",
