        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Call Now - show contact info x 257 OR Text 257 to show contact info for more information. Interested In This Unit? Use this link for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/8zyadb Experience Harlo Apartments 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 1000 square feet Features ✓  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ✓  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✓  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ✓  Controlled access buildings ✓  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ✓  Dishwasher available in select homes ✓  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet Community Features ✓  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ✓  Updater application ✓  Open parking and carports ✓  Flex rental payments ✓  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ✓  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ✓  Pet friendly community ✓  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ✓  Online resident portal ✓  Package receiving ✓  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ✓  Professional onsite management team ✓  On-site resident storage ✓  Easy highway access ✓  BILT payment center Community Info Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity 0hhS83FAXf",
