        "geocode_query": "31499 Mound Road near 13 Mile",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 800 More unit details at: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/k1gh4w Experience Harlo Apartments Call Now - show contact info x 256 OR Text 256 to show contact info to text us.   Community Info Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Residence Features ✩  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ✩  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ✩  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ✩  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✩  Dishwasher available in select homes ✩  Controlled access buildings ✩  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ✩  Updated lighting fixtures throughout Community Features ✩  Online resident portal ✩  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ✩  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ✩  BILT payment center ✩  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ✩  Open parking and carports ✩  Updater application ✩  Easy highway access ✩  Package receiving ✩  Flex rental payments ✩  Pet friendly community ✩  Professional onsite management team ✩  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ✩  On-site resident storage ✩  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity yF5kC1Yj87",
        "phone": "",
