        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Get ready to fall in love with this beautifully updated single-family home bursting with character and modern upgrades! Nestled in a quiet, friendly neighborhood, this home offers the perfect balance of a peaceful retreat and convenient access to downtown Royal Oak. Why You'll Love the Space: Enjoy total peace of mind with a fully modernized interior, including a finished basement, remodeled bathrooms, and the convenience of on-site laundry. Step outside into a low-maintenance yard featuring a privacy fence, garden, and a large shed for extra storage. Stay cozy year-round with a high-efficiency furnace and central A/C system. Unbeatable Location: Leave your car in the driveway! You are just a 7-minute walk to downtown Royal Oak, close to local parks, and minutes from the train station. Experience the very best of Royal Oak right from your doorstep, from local boutiques and trendy dining to front-row vibes for the Dream Cruise and Arts, Beats & Eats. The Details: show contact info",
