        "location": "31597 Harlo Drive",
        "full_address": "31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights, MI",
        "locality": "Madison Heights",
        "geocode_query": "31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post President Madison Apartments 31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Want more info? See the link below: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/o86gpx Call Now - show contact info x 118 OR Text 118 to show contact info to text our team directly. President Madison Apartments 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 820 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Whether you choose a 1 & 2 bedroom floor plan, when you step inside your new home at President Madison near Troy, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of comfort. A large, open-area living room with a picture window gives way to thoughtfully upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets give you the room you need, and central AC and heat put you in control of your environment - no matter what the weather is like outside. Our modern community center, gated pool with lounge furniture, and fitness center are conveniently accessible and open when you need to relax, unwind or blow off steam. Located near the best of what Metro Detroit has to offer, President Madison has exactly what you're looking for in your new home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut* vinyl plank flooring ✧  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✧  Gas Range in all apartment homes ✧  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✧  Dishwashers available in select homes ✧  Carports available ✧  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ✧  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ✧  Resident Storage located on-site ✧  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✧  Secured entrance for each residence ✧  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✧  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✧  Spacious closets ✧  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ✧  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 856 square feet Community Highlights ✧  Carports available ✧  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television ✧  Online Resident Portal ✧  Professional Onsite Management Team ✧  Beautiful, mature landscape ✧  Expansive community center ✧  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ✧  Updater Application ✧  FLEX Rental Payment ✧  On-site resident storage area ✧  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ✧  Package Receiving ✧  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar ✧  BILT Payment Center Driving Directions From I-75N: Exit at 12 Mile Rd. and turn right. Turn left at John R Rd. Pass 13 Mille and you will see Sam's Club on your right. Turn right at the first street after Sam's Club (Irving). Turn left at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. From I-75S: Exit at 14 Mile Rd. and turn left. Turn right at John R Rd. Turn left at Whitcomb (7-11 and target). Turn right at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Equal Housing Opportunity SubV9vlxQbWh",
