        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bedrooms, 1 Bath – Approximately 856 Sq. Ft. Step inside and enjoy a large, open living room with a picture window, upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets provide ample storage, and central AC and heat keep your home comfortable year-round. The community features a modern center, a gated pool with lounge furniture, and a fitness center for relaxation or exercise. Unit Highlights: - Common laundry room with full-size GE washer and dryer - Accent walls in the living area - Secured entrance for each residence - Spacious closets - Kitchen with oak cabinetry, GE white appliances, and dark walnut vinyl plank flooring - Carports available - Satin nickel hardware throughout - Updated lighting - Brick buildings and traditional architecture - Large picture windows with designer blinds - On-site resident storage - Soft hued paint with white paneled doors - Floor plans from 800 to 856 square feet - Gas range in all units - Plush neutral carpet in living room and bedrooms - Dishwashers in select homes Community Highlights: - Expansive community center - Mature landscaping - BILT Payment Center - Professional onsite management - FLEX Rental Payment - Online Resident Portal - Carports available - On-site storage - Internet café with coffee bar - Outdoor swimming pool - Updater Application - Pet-friendly with pet area and nearby dog park - Package receiving - Exercise room with flat-screen TV Location is near major highways and Metro Detroit attractions. Pet policy welcomes cats and small dogs. Feel free to reply with your name and the best way to reach you if you'd like to schedule a tour.",
