        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 1000 Sq. Ft. Use the link below for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/y9q7a0 Call Now - show contact info x 255 OR Text 255 to show contact info to contact us. Experience Harlo Apartments Community Info: Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Features: ‣  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ‣  Dishwasher available in select homes ‣  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ‣  Controlled access buildings ‣  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ‣  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove Community Amenities: ‣  Package receiving ‣  Updater application ‣  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ‣  Open parking and carports ‣  Professional onsite management team ‣  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ‣  BILT payment center ‣  Flex rental payments ‣  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ‣  On-site resident storage ‣  Pet friendly community ‣  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ‣  Easy highway access ‣  Online resident portal ‣  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer Pet Policy: We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements: Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Equal Housing Opportunity 6NpVFVZKy",
