        "locality": "Madison Heights",
        "geocode_query": "00PM Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 625 Sq. Ft. Need more information? Copy this link: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/obljqs Call Now - show contact info x 176 OR Text 176 to show contact info to text our team directly. APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS Community Info: Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home. Features: ‣  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ‣  Heated hallways ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ‣  Indoor mailboxes ‣  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer ‣  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds ‣  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ‣  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ‣  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ‣  On-site resident storage included ‣  Gas range in all apartment homes ‣  Beautiful courtyard views available ‣  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Dishwashers available in select homes ‣  Spacious closets ‣  Walk-in closets in select homes Community Amenities: ‣  Online resident portal ‣  Expansive community clubhouse ‣  Package receiving ‣  BILT payment center ‣  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall ‣  Covered parking ‣  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ‣  On-site resident storage ‣  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ‣  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ‣  Professional onsite management team ‣  Updater application ‣  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ‣  Beautiful, mature landscape ‣  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ‣  Flex rental payments ‣  24-hour maintenance response guarantee Pet Policy: Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Office Hours: Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Equal Housing Opportunity fX2LF6OVbtQ",
