        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Modern Luxury home in Heart of West Bloomfield 7488 Gramercy Circle, West Bloomfield, MI 48322 4750.00 / Month 4 BEDROOMS | 4 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6MzY5ODk3?property=1268105&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/7488-gramercy-circle-west-bloomfield-mi/2bba962d-aa19-4d16-8828-0ca62169e274?source=craigslist Property Description: Indulge in fine design & luxury at the brand-new home in West Bloomfield Township! This stunning rental offering boasts spacious 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a large living area, modern kitchen with an additional loft and recreation area. Spanning over 3200 square feet of living space and a large finished basement with bathroom, bar, recreation area and store. Attached 2-car garage with high-speed EV charging, & open layouts w/ sun-filled interiors. Impeccable custom finishes include beautiful wide-plank flooring, tray ceilings & crown moldings, paneled doors, & high-end lighting fixtures throughout. Open layouts afford easy flow for entertaining w/ large living areas & gorgeous custom kitchen appointed w/ modern 2-toned cabinetry, stone countertops/backsplash plus premium appliances. Generous bedrooms, abundant walk-in closets, & full spa baths w/ frameless showers & infinity floors heighten the allure. All outdoor maintenance is included in the rent. Property Type : Condo Pets : Small Dogs, Cats, Large Dogs Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 4750.00 / Month 4750.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 07/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: No Limit Utilities Included : Sewage Garbage Appliances : Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Refrigerator Washer Microwave Dryer Freezer Range Oven Amenities : Cable Ready Hottub Spa Lawn On Site Laundry Vaulted Ceiling Secure Building Furnished Near Parks Fireplace Garage Bicycle Parking Off Street Parking Wired For Internet Heating & Cooling : Forc