        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Use the link below for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/49eteo Call Now - show contact info x 254 OR Text 254 to show contact info to chat! Experience Harlo Apartments 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 800 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Dishwasher available in select homes ✧  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ✧  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ✧  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ✧  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ✧  Controlled access buildings ✧  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ✧  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet Community Highlights ✧  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ✧  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ✧  Easy highway access ✧  Open parking and carports ✧  Package receiving ✧  Updater application ✧  Online resident portal ✧  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ✧  Flex rental payments ✧  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ✧  BILT payment center ✧  On-site resident storage ✧  Professional onsite management team ✧  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ✧  Pet friendly community Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Equal Housing Opportunity qnjEuWUsdt4h",
