        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Call Now - show contact info x 175 OR Text 175 to show contact info to text our leasing team. Want more info on this unit? See the link (below): https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/8xp6ul APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 800 square feet Features ✓  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✓  Heated hallways ✓  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ✓  Indoor mailboxes ✓  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✓  Gas range in all apartment homes ✓  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✓  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✓  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer ✓  Dishwashers available in select homes ✓  On-site resident storage included ✓  Spacious closets ✓  Walk-in closets in select homes ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ✓  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ✓  Beautiful courtyard views available Community Features ✓  Covered parking ✓  Package receiving ✓  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ✓  BILT payment center ✓  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ✓  Professional onsite management team ✓  24-hour maintenance response guarantee ✓  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ✓  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ✓  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ✓  Flex rental payments ✓  On-site resident storage ✓  Updater application ✓  Expansive community clubhouse ✓  Online resident portal ✓  Beautiful, mature landscape ✓  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall Community Info Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home. Pet Policy Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Office Hours Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity uDzek6F0",
