        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 820 Sq. Ft. Want more info on this unit? See the link (below): https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/94uw4z Call Now - show contact info x 116 OR Text 116 to show contact info to contact our team. President Madison Apartments Community Info: Whether you choose a 1 & 2 bedroom floor plan, when you step inside your new home at President Madison near Troy, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of comfort. A large, open-area living room with a picture window gives way to thoughtfully upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets give you the room you need, and central AC and heat put you in control of your environment - no matter what the weather is like outside. Our modern community center, gated pool with lounge furniture, and fitness center are conveniently accessible and open when you need to relax, unwind or blow off steam. Located near the best of what Metro Detroit has to offer, President Madison has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Features: ‣  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ‣  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ‣  Spacious closets ‣  Gas Range in all apartment homes ‣  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 856 square feet ‣  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ‣  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ‣  Dishwashers available in select homes ‣  Secured entrance for each residence ‣  Resident Storage located on-site ‣  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut* vinyl plank flooring ‣  Carports available ‣  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ‣  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer Community Amenities: ‣  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ‣  On-site resident storage area ‣  Expansive community center ‣  Beautiful, mature landscape ‣  BILT Payment Center ‣  Package Receiving ‣  Updater Application ‣  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television ‣  FLEX Rental Payment ‣  Professional Onsite Management Team ‣  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ‣  Online Resident Portal ‣  Carports available ‣  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar Pet Policy: We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM President Madison Apartments 31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Equal Housing Opportunity 6KfbmIoq",
