        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 27435 Greenfield Road, Southfield, MI 48076 Cambridge Square Apartments in Southfield, Michigan, offers spacious one and two-bedroom floor plans within a lush, park-like setting. Features include covered parking, laundry facilities, and central air conditioning. Cambridge Square provides easy access to local expressways including I-696 and is just minutes from Birmingham, Royal Oak, Berkley and Ferndale and only two miles from both Beaumont and Providence Hospitals. Call us today for your personal tour! Apartment Features: High Speed Internet Access Cable Ready Central Air Conditioning Window Coverings Oversized Closets Dishwasher Hardwood Flooring in Some Areas Linen Closet Dining Room Community Features: Laundry Facility Playground Additional Storage Secured Entry with Intercom Covered Parking Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithm2.com/gvaelkbc/cambridge-square Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
