      "house_ger": {
        "id": "9a1b6805-c0bc-4c0e-8a25-e8978ee2f9f2",
        "name": "Individually-controlled air conditioning units, Covered parking",
        "location": "32000 Concord Drive",
        "mainpic": "23814397-1900-4f9c-8152-590f8277bb02",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Use this link for more information: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/t4ry96 Call Now - show contact info x 136 OR Text 136 to show contact info to text with us. APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 625 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Heated hallways ✧  Walk-in closets in select homes ✧  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✧  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✧  On-site resident storage included ✧  Dishwashers available in select homes ✧  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ✧  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ✧  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✧  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ✧  Spacious closets ✧  Beautiful courtyard views available ✧  Indoor mailboxes ✧  Gas range in all apartment homes ✧  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✧  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer Community Highlights ✧  24-hour maintenance response guarantee ✧  BILT payment center ✧  On-site resident storage ✧  Updater application ✧  Covered parking ✧  Beautiful, mature landscape ✧  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ✧  Package receiving ✧  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ✧  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ✧  Professional onsite management team ✧  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall ✧  Online resident portal ✧  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ✧  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ✧  Flex rental payments ✧  Expansive community clubhouse Office Hours Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Pet Policy Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Equal Housing Opportunity 27s4QQPM",
