        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post President Madison Apartments 31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Call Now - show contact info x 115 OR Text 115 to show contact info to contact us. Want more info on this unit? See the link (below): https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/pn4e3k President Madison Apartments 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 856 square feet Features ✓  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✓  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✓  Carports available ✓  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ✓  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✓  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✓  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ✓  Secured entrance for each residence ✓  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut* vinyl plank flooring ✓  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✓  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ✓  Resident Storage located on-site ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 856 square feet ✓  Spacious closets ✓  Dishwashers available in select homes ✓  Gas Range in all apartment homes Community Features ✓  BILT Payment Center ✓  Professional Onsite Management Team ✓  Carports available ✓  Updater Application ✓  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ✓  Online Resident Portal ✓  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar ✓  On-site resident storage area ✓  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ✓  Package Receiving ✓  Expansive community center ✓  FLEX Rental Payment ✓  Beautiful, mature landscape ✓  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television Community Info Whether you choose a 1 & 2 bedroom floor plan, when you step inside your new home at President Madison near Troy, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of comfort. A large, open-area living room with a picture window gives way to thoughtfully upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets give you the room you need, and central AC and heat put you in control of your environment - no matter what the weather is like outside. Our modern community center, gated pool with lounge furniture, and fitness center are conveniently accessible and open when you need to relax, unwind or blow off steam. Located near the best of what Metro Detroit has to offer, President Madison has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity jw9oKIk5o",
