        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Call Now - show contact info x 253 OR Text 253 to show contact info to contact our team. Use the link below for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/56qdxa Experience Harlo Apartments 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 1000 square feet Features ✓  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ✓  Dishwasher available in select homes ✓  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✓  Controlled access buildings ✓  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ✓  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture ✓  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight Community Features ✓  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ✓  BILT payment center ✓  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ✓  Professional onsite management team ✓  Flex rental payments ✓  On-site resident storage ✓  Easy highway access ✓  Updater application ✓  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ✓  Online resident portal ✓  Package receiving ✓  Open parking and carports ✓  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ✓  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ✓  Pet friendly community Community Info Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity R0p13veEvo",
