        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Maple Grove Apartments 34824 Birch Grove Road, Sterling Heights, MI, 48312 Call Now - show contact info x 125 OR Text 125 to show contact info to text our leasing team. Need more information? Copy this link: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/mwd3h9 APARTMENTS IN SOUTHERN SUBURB OF DETROIT STERLING HEIGHTS 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 1000 square feet Features ✓  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ✓  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ✓  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✓  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ✓  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✓  Resident storage located on-site ✓  Gas range in all apartment homes ✓  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✓  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1000 square feet ✓  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✓  Dishwashers available in select homes ✓  Controlled Access to Building ✓  Walk-in closets ✓  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut vinyl plank flooring ✓  Brick buildings and traditional architecture Community Features ✓  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool and expansive pool deck ✓  Exercise room with flat screen television ✓  Easy access to freeways ✓  Pet friendly - cats and dogs- limited dog approved buildings and restricted breeds do apply. ✓  Professionally landscaped ✓  Easy access to shopping ✓  On-site management ✓  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✓  24-hour Maintenance Response Guarantee ✓  On-line Resident Portal (see Resident Services tab) Community Info Spacious living areas, updated furnishings, and energy efficient appliances are what you’ll find in our one- or two-bedroom floor plans. Maple Grove offers comfort, affordability and convenience in one beautifully manicured, tranquil community. In-home amenities like individually controlled AC and heat, walk-in clos