        "geocode_query": "31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post President Madison Apartments 31597 Harlo Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Interested in more information? Visit link below: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/7wmzbf Call Now - show contact info x 114 OR Text 114 to show contact info to contact us. President Madison Apartments 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath | Approximately 820 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Whether you choose a 1 & 2 bedroom floor plan, when you step inside your new home at President Madison near Troy, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of comfort. A large, open-area living room with a picture window gives way to thoughtfully upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets give you the room you need, and central AC and heat put you in control of your environment - no matter what the weather is like outside. Our modern community center, gated pool with lounge furniture, and fitness center are conveniently accessible and open when you need to relax, unwind or blow off steam. Located near the best of what Metro Detroit has to offer, President Madison has exactly what you're looking for in your new home.   Unit Highlights ✧  Secured entrance for each residence ✧  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✧  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✧  Carports available ✧  Gas Range in all apartment homes ✧  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ✧  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✧  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 856 square feet ✧  Resident Storage located on-site ✧  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut* vinyl plank flooring ✧  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ✧  Dishwashers available in select homes ✧  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✧  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ✧  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ✧  Spacious closets Community Highlights ✧  Carports available ✧  BILT Payment Center ✧  FLEX Rental Payment ✧  Expansive community center ✧  Beautiful, mature landscape ✧  Online Resident Portal ✧  On-site resident storage area ✧  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television ✧  Professional Onsite Management Team ✧  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ✧  Package Receiving ✧  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ✧  Updater Application ✧  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar Driving Directions From I-75N: Exit at 12 Mile Rd. and turn right. Turn left at John R Rd. Pass 13 Mille and you will see Sam's Club on your right. Turn right at the first street after Sam's Club (Irving). Turn left at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. From I-75S: Exit at 14 Mile Rd. and turn left. Turn right at John R Rd. Turn left at Whitcomb (7-11 and target). Turn right at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Equal Housing Opportunity UdlpbA5T2l",
