        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 800 Sq. Ft. Interested In This Unit? Use this link for more details: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/ktkyzn Call Now - show contact info x 95 OR Text 95 to show contact info to text with us. APARTMENTS IN MADISON HEIGHTS Community Info: Welcome home. Open floor plans and natural light is what you'll find when you choose a new home at Lexington Village. Whether you decide on a one- or two- bedroom concept, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into an newly upgraded, contemporary kitchen. High-quality appliances, wood-like vinyl flooring, optional dishwasher, and stylish new cabinets are just a few of the amenities available to you. Spacious closets, individual AC and heat controls, on-site laundry and indoor mailboxes make your life convenient and comfortable, while shared community features that include a clubhouse, swimming pool and fitness center make living at Lexington Village an easy choice for your new home. Features: ‣  Individually-controlled air conditioning units ‣  Dishwashers available in select homes ‣  Heated hallways ‣  Gas range in all apartment homes ‣  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ‣  Indoor mailboxes ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 625 to 850 square feet ‣  Common laundry room in each building with full size washer and dryer ‣  On-site resident storage included ‣  Spacious closets ‣  Gas/heat, water, and trash included in flat monthly rate ‣  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ‣  Walk-in closets in select homes ‣  Beautiful courtyard views available ‣  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Large picturesque windows fitted with designer selected blinds Community Amenities: ‣  Expansive community clubhouse ‣  Pet friendly community with well-designed pet area and less than a mile away from city dog park ‣  On-site resident storage ‣  Updater application ‣  24-hour maintenance response guarantee ‣  Controlled access and intercom system for building entry ‣  Beautiful, mature landscape ‣  Community laundry facility with industrial sized machines ‣  Professional onsite management team ‣  Package receiving ‣  Walking distance to AMC Theater and Oakland Mall ‣  State-of-the-art fitness center with flat screen televisions ‣  Flex rental payments ‣  Covered parking ‣  Easy access to I-75 and I-696 ‣  Online resident portal ‣  BILT payment center Pet Policy: Lexington Village Apartments offers pet friendly apartments in Madison Heights and welcomes both cats and dogs. You'll find beautiful green spaces where your dog can run and play. In addition, your dog can run free and meet new friends at the nearby Red Oak Dog Park. We are one of the few communities in the area to welcome your large dog! We have a limit of 2 pets under 25 lbs each or one large pet without a weight limit. Some breed restrictions apply. We're confident your pet will love living at Lexington Village Apartments as much as our human neighbors do! Office Hours: Monday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Tuesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Wednesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Thursday: 9:00AM-7:00PM Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-2:00PM Lexington Village Apartments 32000 Concord Drive, Madison Heights, MI, 48071 Equal Housing Opportunity x4Mzy4UQDMo",
