        "geocode_query": "31597 Harlo Drive",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 856 See our property details here: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/16nsll President Madison Apartments Call Now - show contact info x 113 OR Text 113 to show contact info to text our team directly.   Community Info Whether you choose a 1 & 2 bedroom floor plan, when you step inside your new home at President Madison near Troy, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of comfort. A large, open-area living room with a picture window gives way to thoughtfully upgraded kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, and a gas stove. Walk-in closets give you the room you need, and central AC and heat put you in control of your environment - no matter what the weather is like outside. Our modern community center, gated pool with lounge furniture, and fitness center are conveniently accessible and open when you need to relax, unwind or blow off steam. Located near the best of what Metro Detroit has to offer, President Madison has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Residence Features ✩  Gas Range in all apartment homes ✩  Beautifully designed kitchen featuring oak cabinetry, GE white appliances and dark walnut* vinyl plank flooring ✩  Dishwashers available in select homes ✩  Secured entrance for each residence ✩  Large picture windows fitted with designer selected blinds ✩  Carports available ✩  Spacious closets ✩  Accent walls in living area of apartment home ✩  Common laundry room with full size GE wash and dryer ✩  Soft hued paint accented with white paneled doors ✩  Updated lighting throughout the apartment home ✩  Brick buildings and traditional architecture ✩  Satin nickel hardware throughout residence ✩  Resident Storage located on-site ✩  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 856 square feet ✩  Spacious living room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet Community Features ✩  BILT Payment Center ✩  FLEX Rental Payment ✩  Online Resident Portal ✩  Carports available ✩  Package Receiving ✩  Expansive community center ✩  Professional Onsite Management Team ✩  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ✩  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ✩  On-site resident storage area ✩  Updater Application ✩  Beautiful, mature landscape ✩  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar ✩  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Driving Directions From I-75N: Exit at 12 Mile Rd. and turn right. Turn left at John R Rd. Pass 13 Mille and you will see Sam's Club on your right. Turn right at the first street after Sam's Club (Irving). Turn left at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. From I-75S: Exit at 14 Mile Rd. and turn left. Turn right at John R Rd. Turn left at Whitcomb (7-11 and target). Turn right at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity hIu7fU0hVYb",
