ceiving ✩  Expansive community center ✩  Professional Onsite Management Team ✩  Beautifully designed outdoor swimming pool ✩  Pet-friendly community with a well-designed pet area, close to a city dog park ✩  On-site resident storage area ✩  Updater Application ✩  Beautiful, mature landscape ✩  Internet café with gourmet coffee bar ✩  Professionally equipped exercise room with flat screen television Pet Policy We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at President Madison. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees, and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore President Madison with you. Driving Directions From I-75N: Exit at 12 Mile Rd. and turn right. Turn left at John R Rd. Pass 13 Mille and you will see Sam's Club on your right. Turn right at the first street after Sam's Club (Irving). Turn left at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. From I-75S: Exit at 14 Mile Rd. and turn left. Turn right at John R Rd. Turn left at Whitcomb (7-11 and target). Turn right at the next main street, Harlo. President Madison Apartments is in the apartment building 31597 with a blue and white sign in front. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity hIu7fU0hVYb",
