        "geocode_query": "00PM Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 1000 Sq. Ft. Follow This Link for More Information: https://wwwbeztakcom.gotoapt.com/zj0xtc Call Now - show contact info x 251 OR Text 251 to show contact info to text us. Experience Harlo Apartments Community Info: Step inside our one- or two-bedroom open-concept floor plan apartments and experience the peace and tranquility of Harlo. You'll be greeted by large windows that let the natural sunlight in, and all the amenities of modern living; individually controlled AC and heat, plush carpet, generous closet space and an updated, ready-to-entertain kitchen, complete with oak cabinets and gas stove. If that weren't enough, your new home comes complete with beautiful views of a lush courtyard, access to a private swimming pool with an open sun deck and reclining lounge chairs, and updated fitness center with flat screen TV. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, Harlo Apartments in Macomb County has exactly what you're looking for in your new home. Features: ‣  Controlled access buildings ‣  Dishwasher available in select homes ‣  Spacious living room, dining room and bedrooms featuring plush neutral carpet ‣  Well-designed kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and gas stove ‣  Well-designed floor plans ranging from 800 to 1,000 square feet ‣  Large picture windows allow floods of natural sunlight ‣  Updated lighting fixtures throughout ‣  Red brick buildings and traditional architecture Community Amenities: ‣  Beautiful, lush grounds and courtyards with mature landscaping ‣  BILT payment center ‣  Near shopping, dining and entertainment venues ‣  Pet friendly community ‣  Flex rental payments ‣  On-site resident storage ‣  Online resident portal ‣  Updater application ‣  Common laundry room with full size washer and dryer ‣  Professionally-equipped exercise room with flat screen televisions ‣  Resort-style swimming pool with expansive sun deck ‣  Easy highway access ‣  Package receiving ‣  Open parking and carports ‣  Professional onsite management team Pet Policy: We are very happy to welcome your cats and small dogs as members of our community at Harlo Apartments. Just down the street you'll find wonderful dog parks and walking trails, or stay close to home and enjoy the lush landscape, mature trees and tranquil open spaces. If you'd like to schedule a tour, be sure to bring your best friend along so they can explore Harlo Apartments with you. Income Requirements: Recent 30 days of pay stubs to meet 2.5 times the rent Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Harlo Apartments 31499 Mound Road, Warren, MI, 48092 Equal Housing Opportunity HI5fewnobo0",
