        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Infinity Park Apartment & Townhome are located on the service drive of a major freeway 1/96 & Telegraph intersection with plenty of public transportation such as (D.DOT, SMART BUS) routes nearby, public school district, local restaurants/ businesses and major shopping centers. In addition, we offer: *Onsite Maintenance *Onsite Guard at the Gate *Appliance Include (Refrigerator, Stove) *Professional Staff *Gated Community *Trash Removal Featuring a spacious 2 Bedroom Townhome with 900 sqf of living space for $995 plus water. the security deposit is 1x the monthly rent for qualified applicants. We're asking that you earn 3x the monthly rent, have been working your current job for at least 6 months long, can provide proof of income (4 current check stub) we also ask that all adults applying provide a valid I.D & Social Security Card, we ask that all adults applying have no evictions on your credit report, our application fee is $39.00 per adult applying... Any questions please call Natalie show contact info Eddie show contact info CLICK THE LINK TO APPLY http://www.infinitypark.net/",
